Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說去喝茶沒想到去喝真正的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}中城不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}羽場也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}澤木口也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我認為不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}社交辭令就就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼讓我聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他們哪裡不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}首先是中城學長
